0:08:32.000Z","msg":"第4集隻八爪魚做乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘔心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"妮娜係靈媒<br />\n隻八爪魚應該係外星生物<br />\n相傳八爪魚係高智商嘅外星生物<br />\nOld Night係少數願意同人類溝通嘅<br />\n而佢又知道OA嘅存在，個37秒flash可能係S3嘅key"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"八爪魚係高智商外星生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係未聽過wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪陰謀論個d野有講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:16:22.000Z","msg":"八爪魚有高 IQ，比其他無脊椎動物更聰明。至於佢哋有幾聰明啲生物學家重拗緊 [3][4][5]，逃出迷宮同解決問題嘅實驗表明八爪魚有短同長期記憶。衰在短命，限制八爪魚最終學到幾多。有人懷疑八爪魚嘅行為係自己學返嚟，唔係本能，雖然證明唔到。八爪魚同佢哋老竇老母冇乜兩句，佢哋嘅行為唔係喺父母學返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n八爪魚有個好複雜嘅神經系統，三份一嘅神經細胞集中喺個腦度，其餘嘅三份二都喺啲爪嘅神經線度，形成高度敏感嘅器官。好似模仿八爪魚識得將啲爪擺出個樣，嚟扮第二啲海裏面嘅生物。<br />\n<br />\n喺實驗室，八爪魚俾人經過訓練之後，識得認物件形狀同排次序。亦有報告話八爪魚重識學返啲人做過嘅嘢，好似開樽蓋咁[6]。此外，八爪魚重有「玩」嘅行為：例如八爪魚噴水整郁半浮沈嘅藥丸樽，令個樽喺水度氹氹轉[7]。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家相信，當八爪魚於緊張狀態，會食咗自己嘅手臂，但好少有人研究呢種唔正常嘅「自我摧殘行為」（self-cannibalism/autophagy），有人估計原因可能同八爪魚體內一啲病毒有關，影響到八爪魚嘅神經系統[未記出處或冇根據]。<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wiki"},{"pid":"d5c36b64f18c6c1d7f61163f8e44f6b81034237b","tid":1071622,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db1b058f3c935adb856ba8522a1b2f79bd726e8f","tid":1071622,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d849641d321c2b817ea47238768c5f8aa8d21377","tid":1071622,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0bb0737af63d3dc3d617d2e5eaacd2cd127b5a0","tid":1071622,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"第4集隻八爪魚做乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘔心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"妮娜係靈媒<br />\n隻八爪魚應該係外星生物<br />\n相傳八爪魚係高智商嘅外星生物<br />\nOld Night係少數願意同人類溝通嘅<br />\n而佢又知道OA嘅存在，個37秒flash可能係S3嘅key"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"八爪魚係高智商外星生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係未聽過wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪陰謀論個d野有講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:23:29.000Z","msg":"八爪魚/章魚嘅DNA喺地球無近親/相似、<br />\n人類嘅dna同猩猩、豬好似<br />\n同埋八爪魚嘅生理結構同其他海洋生物都好唔同，再加上佢嘅智商，所以就有八爪魚係外星人嘅講法"},{"pid":"e0bcbd6f5ef6a51bcb8da198c10b4c36f31a3ca6","tid":1071622,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"原來主角個養父現實係年尾行咗......"},{"pid":"42948b6d03336ef519525f7c0d905a8c69359d77","tid":1071622,"uid":29342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/the-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2019%2F03%2Fthe-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3LccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=f5c33cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/the-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998/</a><br />\n<br />\nSeason 2 結局解釋，小心劇透"},{"pid":"b15b9914d91d51e4a47da5bdb313da1f50ec84af","tid":1071622,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42948b6d03336ef519525f7c0d905a8c69359d77","tid":1071622,"uid":29342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/the-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2019%2F03%2Fthe-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3LccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=f5c33cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/the-oa-season-2-ending-spoilers-1202052998/</a><br />\n<br />\nSeason 2 結局解釋，小心劇透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"睇到ep6, 我覺得個幾個配角仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2e0a78afe61669d5e8927bf72975f4b02bbf99","tid":1071622,"uid":80093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0bcbd6f5ef6a51b